data.description: Welcome to this stunning two-story, 4 bedrooms home that offers a large open concept living space, tons of storage, and spacious bedrooms. On the main floor, you have a spacious kitchen and a center island overlooking the family room. On the first floor you will also find the formal dining room, powder bath, pantry, a covered patio and a large primary bedroom. The primary bedroom has a large bathroom with double sinks, a garden tub, shower and a walk-in closet. Upstairs you will find the game room, three bedrooms as well as a media room. Schedule your visit today!
